# 1ï¸âƒ£ API ENDPOINT DESIGN (Exact & Practical)

## ğŸ” AUTHENTICATION APIs

### Register

```
POST /api/auth/register
```

**Body**

```json
{
  "name": "Arjun",
  "email": "arjun@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "student"
}
```

### Login

```
POST /api/auth/login
```

**Response**

```json
{
  "token": "jwt_token_here",
  "role": "student"
}
```

---

## ğŸ‘¤ USER APIs

### Get Profile

```
GET /api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

### Update Profile

```
PUT /api/users/profile
```

---

## ğŸ¼ COURSE APIs

### Create Course (Teacher)

```
POST /api/courses
```

```json
{
  "title": "Karnatic Vocal â€“ Beginner",
  "description": "Basics of Karnatic music",
  "price": 999
}
```

### Get All Courses

```
GET /api/courses
```

### Get Teacherâ€™s Courses

```
GET /api/courses/my
```

---

## ğŸ“… CLASS / SESSION APIs

### Schedule Live Class

```
POST /api/classes
```

```json
{
  "course_id": 1,
  "start_time": "2026-01-10 18:00",
  "duration": 60
}
```

### Get Upcoming Classes

```
GET /api/classes/upcoming
```

---

## ğŸ¥ LIVE MEETING APIs (Agora / 100ms)

### Generate Meeting Token

```
POST /api/meetings/token
```

```json
{
  "class_id": 5,
  "role": "host"
}
```

### Join Class

```
POST /api/classes/join
```

---

## ğŸ§ RECORDINGS APIs

### Save Recording

```
POST /api/recordings
```

### Get Recordings

```
GET /api/recordings/:course_id
```

---

## ğŸ“ ATTENDANCE APIs

### Mark Attendance

```
POST /api/attendance
```

### View Attendance (Teacher)

```
GET /api/attendance/:class_id
```

